nodes.text: Tino was the flatmate of Ren S'orn. While he was working in a warehouse, the bounty hunter Ona Nobis attempted to kill him, but the Padawan Obi-Wan Kenobi and Astri Oddo were able to save him. Once the situation had calmed down, he gave them information on how to find Jenna Zan Arbor and Qui-Gon Jinn.
